<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Re:View - 오답 게시판</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="logo">Re:View</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/board">게시판</a>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/write">오답작성</a>
                    <a href="/profile">마이페이지</a>
                    <a href="/logout">로그아웃</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/login">로그인</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">
            <h1>오답 게시판</h1>
            <% if (user) { %>
                <a href="/write" class="btn btn-primary" style="padding: 10px 20px; font-size: 0.9rem;">새 오답 작성</a>
            <% } %>
        </div>

        <div class="notes-list">
            <% if (notes && notes.length > 0) { %>
                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px;">
                    <% notes.forEach(note => { %>
                        <a href="/post/<%= note.id %>" class="card">
                            <span class="tag">
                                <%= note.type_name || '기타' %>
                            </span>
                            <h3><%= note.title %></h3>
                            <p><%= note.solution.substring(0, 80) %><%= note.solution.length > 80 ? '...' : '' %></p>
                            <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;">
                                <span>작성자: <%= note.username || '익명' %></span>
                                <span><%= new Date(note.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %></span>
                            </div>
                        </a>
                    <% }); %>
                </div>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="card" style="text-align: center; padding: 60px;">
                    <p>아직 등록된 오답 노트가 없습니다. 첫 번째 노트를 작성해 보세요!</p>
                    <a href="/write" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 20px;">오답 작성하기</a>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
